SOLUTION

We followed the below steps to resolve the issue.
 
· Created a new Secure Store Service Application
· Select Generate New Key to enter the Pass Phrase >> Created Secure Store Target Application specifying Target Application ID, Target Application Type as Group
· Add the Farm account under Target Application Administrator and Domain users group under Members
· Set Credentials for Target Application and selected SA account 
· Edit the External Content Type Connection and selected the new Target Application ID 
· Access the External Lists and it was able to fetch the metadata from the database.
